#, no-wrap
msgid "APP_ENV=dev ./yii rbac:init\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/security/authorization.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"> If you don't want to hardcode what users have certain roles, don't put `->assign()` calls into the command. Instead,\n"
"  create either UI or console command to manage assignments.\n"
msgstr ""
"> 如果您不想硬编码哪些用户具有某些角色，请不要在命令中放入 `->assign()` 调用。相反，\n"
"  创建 UI 或控制台命令来管理分配。\n"

#. type: Title ####
